        "subject": "LU-1346 libcfs: cleanup libcfs primitive (linux-prim.h)",
        "message": "LU-1346 libcfs: cleanup libcfs primitive (linux-prim.h)\n\nUse the sed script to cleanup libcfs primitives (linux-prim.h)\n\nSome other changes:\n1. Move some kernel version compatible macros to portals_compat25.h\n2. Remove __wait_event_timeout definition\n3. Change cfs_waitq_wait_event_timeout and\n   cfs_waitq_wait_event_interruptible_timeout to linux kernel API\n4. Replace some function definitions in linux-prim.c as macros in\n   linux-prim.h\n\nSigned-off-by: Liu Xuezhao <xuezhao.liu@emc.com>\nChange-Id: I3a2948fa62881ff0e3bbdafcaacc26fa278e52e2\n"
